elements.name: Como usuario quiero modificar un tag

steps.name: I navigate to page "http://localhost:2368/ghost/#/signin"
I enter "ghost-author@example.com" into input field having id "ember8"
I enter "Pruebas10automatizadas" into input field having id "ember10"
I click on element having id "ember12"
I should see text "Tags"
I navigate to page "http://localhost:2368/ghost/#/tags"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-btn-primary"
I enter "Kraken Tag For Update" into input field having id "tag-name"
I enter "Kraken Tag for Update Description" into input field having id "tag-description"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-btn-primary"
I should see text "Delete Tag"
I navigate to page "http://localhost:2368/ghost/#/tags"
I should see text "Kraken Tag For Update"
I navigate to page "http://localhost:2368/ghost/#/tags/kraken-tag-for-update"
I enter "Kraken Tag is Updated" into input field having id "tag-name"
I enter "Kraken Tag is Updated Description" into input field having id "tag-description"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-btn-primary"
I should see text "Delete Tag"
I navigate to page "http://localhost:2368/ghost/#/tags"
I wait for 2 seconds
